      <title>美国新屋销售下降；中位价格为 2-1/2 年来最低</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-new-home-sales-unexpectedly-fall-february-2024-03-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2 月份抵押贷款利率上升后，美国新单户住宅销量意外下降，但由于市场上二手房长期短缺，基本趋势依然强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-new-home-sales-unexpectedly-fall-february-2024-03-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 14:19:54 GMT</pubDate>
